{
  "name": "Pre-Shell Safety Check",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "셸 명령 실행 전 안전성을 검증합니다",
  "when": {
    "type": "preToolUse",
    "toolTypes": [
      "shell"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Before this shell command, check:\n1. DESTRUCTIVE — Does it delete files (rm -rf), drop databases, or modify production resources? If yes, BLOCK and ask for confirmation.\n2. LONG-RUNNING — Is it a dev server (npm run server:dev), watch mode, or interactive command that won't terminate? If yes, BLOCK and suggest using background process or manual execution.\n3. SIDE EFFECTS — Does it install global packages, modify system config, or push to remote? If yes, warn the user.\n4. DATABASE — Does it run migrations or seeds on production? If yes, BLOCK and require explicit confirmation.\nOnly report issues found. If all checks pass, proceed silently."
  }
}
